<item>
            <title>[LU-18019] Need to check FORCE_LARGE_NID in load_modules_local</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18019</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need to tweak the use of FORCE_LARGE_NID in test-framework.sh in order for it to work transparently with other test suites. Most test suites start LNet via load_modules_local, but FORCE_LARGE_NID is not checked or enforced on this path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
